1	/**
2	 * Queue worker — processes analysis_queue items one at a time.
3	 *
4	 * Called as a detached subprocess spawned by `session-end` after enqueue.
5	 * Resets stale processing items first, then claims and runs pending items
6	 * until the queue is empty.
7	 *
8	 * Worker spawned with CODE_INSIGHTS_HOOK_ACTIVE=1 in env so that
9	 * ClaudeNativeRunner does not re-trigger this hook recursively.
10	 */
11	
